{"tid":878180,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"依家啲港女 有咁好嘅男朋友係身邊都唔識珍惜","createTime":"2018-10-27T02:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T18:52:54.000Z","uid":198777,"like":87,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9de780bb8c4b2f48fe8388ac3bd3b53cc130456a","tid":878180,"uid":198777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:27:00.000Z","msg":"當初鐘意你嘅時候 講到咩缺點都會包容你<br />\n漸漸一齊耐左 自己啲缺點開始暴露晒出嚟嘅時候<br />\n又想你為左佢而改變 <br />\n當初講又話好欣賞你做番自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有唔知點解咁貪新鮮感 <br />\n成日係交友app到話識新朋友姐 我又無出軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個專一到爆嘅男朋友 又想你做壞男人<br />\n又講乜春男人唔壞 女人唔愛 你唔明架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要成日圍威喂同班姊妹講自己男朋友有幾蠢幾廢<br />\n搞到自己男朋友乜野面子都無晒<br />\n班八婆仲要懶係好了解人地段關係 <br />\n叫晒分手咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本尊重識唔識？<br />\n你平時做錯野 男人會唔會同自己班兄弟笑鳩你？<br />\n明明自己啲性格都唔撚好得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港男 自己好自為之啦 <br />\n有啲咁嘅港女女朋友好飛左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba21cff2209e1467a959fd3fde2f7011b044a49","tid":878180,"uid":198777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9a803462a3836b0bb81a8ac0a3f18b3fe24f94","tid":878180,"uid":109655,"like":40,"dislike":4,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:40:15.000Z","msg":"有啲港男都唔識珍惜女朋友"},{"pid":"a3974f75f99bf8a8a1f7d3f9e4ba6dd728fd7132","tid":878180,"uid":60731,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:42:00.000Z","msg":"女人只愛一個佢想愛的男人<br />\n你提到的內容8成都係藉口<br />\n你專唔專一佢只會發燒嗰陣